Package com.axelor.studio.db

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChartFilter
    Object to store filter conditions used in chart and ViewCalcuation object.
    ChartOperator
    Object to store operators like =, !=, >, < ..etc with fields types in which they can be use.
    FieldType
    Object to store field types like OneToMany,ManyToOne,BigDecimal,..etc.
    MenuEditor
    This object store edited menu with menu attributes.
    ModelImporter
    This class is use to import models in xlsx format.
    ModuleManager
    Object to export and import studio modules in zip format.
    ModuleRecorder
    General object to apply changes done in view and models.
    ReportBuilder
    This class use to generate template from selected view and also add button in view.
    RightManagement
    This object store group and permission for model and fields.
    ViewButton
    This object store button and its attributes.
    ViewCalculationLine
    This class use to add custom calcuation in view.
    ViewEditor
    This is main class to store all edited views.
    ViewField
    This object store custom view field attributes like, readonlyIf,widget,colSpan,onChange .etc.
    ViewPanel
    This object store panels of form view.
    Wkf
    This class is main workflow class.
    WkfNode
    This is workflow node and it represents status of object linked with workflow.
    WkfTracking
    This object store workflow realted tracking information for an object.
    WkfTrackingLine
    This object store workflow tracking of status and time spent on particular status.
    WkfTrackingTime
    It store total time spent on particular status.
    WkfTrackingTotal
    It store number of time(count) particular status used for an object.
    WkfTransition
    This object store transition information of nodes of workflow.
